ck to avoid creating a duplicate auth node\0ain the Soroban authorization tree.\0a\0a# Safety\0aOnly use this variant if you have already called `require_auth()` on this address\0ain the current contract invocation. Misuse may allow unauthorized fee deductions.\00\00\00\00\08Verified\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\14OAppError: 2000-2099\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09OAppError\00\00\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0eInvalidOptions\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06NoPeer\00\00\00\00\07\d1\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08OnlyPeer\00\00\07\d2\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\13ZroTokenUnavailable\00\00\00\07\d3\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07OFTSent\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\08oft_sent\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04guid\00\00\03\ee\00\00\00 \00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07dst_eid\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04from\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0eamount_sent_ld\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\12amount_received_ld\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0bOFTReceived\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\0coft_received\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04guid\00\00\03\ee\00\00\00 \00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07src_eid\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02to\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\12amount_received_ld\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0fMsgInspectorSet\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\11msg_inspector_set\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09inspector\00\00\00\00\00\03\e8\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0aOFTStorage\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0cDecimalsDiff\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05Token\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0cMsgInspector\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\13OFTError: 3000-3099\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08OFTError\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0eInvalidAddress\00\00\00\00\0b\b8\00\00